      "TW": ">>> 在橋上阻止殭屍！！<<<"
    }
  },
  ">>> Let's move forward to the tower! <<<": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": ">>> 今度はタワーへ進みましょう！ <<<",
